## East Midlands Railway

This article pertains to the current entity operating the East Midlands rail franchise. For historical context regarding its predecessor, please refer to [East Midlands Trains](/East_Midlands_Trains).

### East Midlands Railway

**(Class 222](/British_Rail_Class_222) at [Nottingham](/Nottingham_railway_station) railway station, adorned in the distinctive EMR Intercity livery)**

